channel.title: SupremeScape
channel.description:
WEBSITE: [url=http://www.supremescape.enjin.com]www.supremescape.enjin.com[/url]
Supremescape is a server made and created by khenz (credit to jake for the source) also know as Jc fire. We strive to offer our player base the best and funnest content we can add. So we are constantly adding more content at all times! are desperately in need of staff since launch was today 3/16/14. We offer alot to our players outside the server itself. Including neat Forums, and soon to come and anticipated Auto-Donation! Hope you enjoy the server from Supreme!
Features:
- 11 Custom bosses - 25/25 Skills working - Prestige system up to 10 prestiges - Hans gives veteran capes based on your online time - 2 Quests - All the Matrix minigames and 3 others made by me - Use the sawmill to make planks and use these to create the nicest furniture - Dungeoneering where you can choose what you want to kill (Har'lakk the Riftsplitter or his minions) - Loyalty Points & Pk Points - The Abyss 100% like RS - Full Living Rock Caverns - Clue Scrolls - Over 20 NPC caves - Penguin Hide and Seek - 100% Bird’s Nests like RS
And much more to discover in the world of Supremescape
